videos.description: Chad President finds Justin Hobbs for a 35-yard touchdown to give Tulsa a 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: Tulsa's President finds Hobbs for TD

videos.description: Isaiah Wright runs for a 47-yard gain to flip field position for Temple.
videos.headline: Wright gashes Tulsa D for big run

videos.description: Frank Nutile hits Adonis Jennings for a 28-yard touchdown to give the Owls a 10-7 lead in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Jennings' TD reclaims lead for Temple

videos.description: Keith Kirkwood's 51-yard catch and run puts the Owls in Tulsa territory.
videos.headline: Temple' Kirkwood explodes for big gain

videos.description: Ryquell Armstead's 9-yard touchdown run gives them a 17-7 lead in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Armstead's TD run extends Temple's lead

videos.description: Frank Nutile connects to Adonis Jennings for a 65-yard gain to set up first-and-goal for Temple.
videos.headline: Temple's Nutile finds Jennings for huge gain

videos.description: David Hood score from 1-yard out to make it a 24-10 lead for Temple in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Hood's TD extends Temple's lead

videos.description: Temple's Derrek Thomas intercepts Will Hefley III deep in Temple territory to stop the Tulsa drive.
videos.headline: Thomas with INT for Temple

videos.description: Frank Nutile hits Keith Kirkwood for a 2-yard touchdown to extend the lead 31-13 in the second quarter.
